title: Mathworks Matlab R2016a Linux x64
description:
Its a working version of Matlab R2016a 64 bits for Linux/Unix, with crack included.

Originally from here: http://www.torrentxhulk.com/software/691506-mathworks-matlab-r2016a-linux.html

The installation instructions was in a indecipherable language. So I've simplified installation and made my README.txt version of it.

It was tested successfully in Debian GNU/Linux version 8 (Jessie) on 13-April-2016.

Enjoy! :)
